    %h1 Develop self updating Mac app in 5 minutes!
    %p.lead You want to focus on your app, we get it! That's why I prepared this super easy way to handle automatic updates for all your users!
    %p
      %a.btn.btn-lg.btn-success{:href => url('/auth/facebook')} Try it out with Facebook login
